# CF Pages _redirects — proxy all non-asset requests to the Worker (SSR + JSON API)
# The Worker serves:
#   GET /               → SSR home HTML
#   GET /:city          → SSR city feed HTML
#   GET /:city/posts/:id → SSR post detail HTML
#   /api/*              → JSON API

/api/*  https://kotakotadev-api.kotakota-developer.workers.dev/api/:splat  200
/*      https://kotakotadev-api.kotakota-developer.workers.dev/:splat      200
